{"id": 237074246, "title": "Trump Is Bragging About Endorsements from Black People. He Paid Some.", "text": "\u201cIn March of 1987, this situation was brought to light, and it was confessed and repented of. I submitted myself to the Elders of Shady Grove Church and the young lady\u2019s father. They asked me to step out of ministry and receive counseling and freedom ministry, which I did. Since that time, I have walked in purity and accountability in this area.\u201d Morris neglected to mention in his statement that Clemishire was 12 at the time the abuse started. He also does not mention apologizing to her directly. Gateway Church said that Morris underwent a two-year \u201crestoration process\u201d following a \u201cmoral failure,\u201d in a statement to WFAA.", "summary": "<html><head></head><body><p>Donald Trump\u2019s campaign announced the creation of a new conservative coalition&nbsp; over the weekend: Black Americans for Trump. But he failed to mention that at least three of his new endorsers are on the Trump family payroll.</p><p><span>Dozens of prominent Black Americans appeared on the </span><a href=\"https://www.newsweek.com/full-list-black-americans-trump-coalition-partners-1913346\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">list</a><span> released Saturday, from former Georgia State Representative Vernon Jones to former NFL safety Jack Brewer. But the names of three former staffers for the RNC and the Trump campaign also, curiously, found their way into the coalition.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>They include former RNC official Gina Barr (who is currently titled as the Trump campaign\u2019s Executive Director of Black Coalitions), Trump campaign spokesman Janiyah Thomas, and senior Trump advisor Lynne Patton\u2014who has received more than $233,000 in \u201cpayroll\u201d disbursements from the Trump campaig", "url": "https://newrepublic.com/post/182822/trump-bragging-endorsements-black-people-paid", "image": "https://images.newrepublic.com/961d8c6d9880d23328087c528a5c89becf53da06.jpeg?w=1200&h=630&crop=faces&fit=crop&fm=jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-18 00:13:47", "author": "Ellie Quinlan Houghtaling,Joe Biden", "authors": ["Ellie Quinlan Houghtaling", "Joe Biden"], "language": "en", "source_country": "US", "sentiment": -0.079}